# DWM
ALT p           dmenu
ALT Enter       st
ALT 1,2...9     tags
ALT t           tiling mode
ALT f           floating mode
ALT m           monockle mode

# Color Picker
Alt c             Color Pick

# LockScreen
Super l           Lock Screen
Ctrl Alt l        Lock Screen

# Screenshot
PrtSc             shot now
Super PrtSc       shot in 3
Shift PrtSc       shot in 5
Ctrl PrtSc        shot wind
Alt PrtSc         shot area

# Power Modes
# https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Lenovo_ThinkPad_X1_Carbon_(Gen_9)#Performance_modes
FN l          Lowpower Mode
FN m          Balanced Mode
FN h          Performance Mode

# Vim
Ctrl n          Nerd Tree
Ctrl W - h,l    Switch splits 
Ctrl W - T      Tab
g - t,T         Next,Prev Tab
